            "title": "港股開市︱初段回吐 恒指跌199點報22777點",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">港股開市初段回吐，恒生指數開市報22777點，跌199點或0.87%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒生科技指數開報5576點，跌62點或1.12%；國企指數以8394點開市，跌81點或0.96%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/03/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股2.png.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/03/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股2.png.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">重磅股今早於競價時段個別發展，將於中午派成績表的滙控(00005)開報87.78元，再升0.63%；昨天收市後公布勝市場預期業績的百度(09888)，今早則開報88.65元，跌1.72%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">應在明日派成績表的多家科企中，阿里巴巴(09988)，今早開報123.7元，跌2.06%；網易(09999)開報163.9元，跌0.97%；聯想(00992)開報12.34元，跌1.75%；嗶哩嗶哩(09626)開報163元，跌%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：滙控官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/bplib_20230703-172008__source-web_00005.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：滙控官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/bplib_20230703-172008__source-web_00005.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：滙控官網</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">昨收市後發盈警的蒙牛乳業(02319)，今早於競價時段不跌反升，開報16.06元，升2.69%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">美國擬最快於4月2日加徵進口汽車關稅，稅率約25%，在港上市車股跌多於升。理想汽車(02015)開報101元，跌1.75%；蔚來(09866)開報34.65元，更跌2.39%；吉利汽車(00175)跌0.45%，開17.68元；比亞迪(01211)則企穩於365.6元開市；小鵬汽車(09868)更逆市升1.83%，報69.6元。</p>\n\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：小鵬汽車官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/03/20240312_FI_source-web_小鵬汽車4.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：小鵬汽車官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/03/20240312_FI_source-web_小鵬汽車4.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：小鵬汽車官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">兩隻今早先後公布配股集資的半新股，今早股價均向下。晶泰控股(02228)開報6.35元，跌2.01%；黑芝麻智能(02533)開報25.45元，3.23%。</p>\n</div>",
